Class TheHuman

  • java.lang.Object
    • enemies.Enemy
      • enemies.TheHuman
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, Renderable, Tickable

    public class TheHuman
extends Enemy
    TheHuman is a class for modeling the human in the Crab Save game. It is called "TheHuman" for reasons no one can explain. The existence of its name is utterly inexplicable, from a certain point of view. Q.E.D.
    Author:
    abraham
